      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think i don\u0027t understand semantics of VM record (instance in DS). I think it\u0027d be great to document this next in vms.go.\n1) when is actual GCE VM created/destroyed vs VM record lifetime?\n   ie, should this immediately try to spawn a new VM, or should it postpone a TQ task to do so?\n   or do you expect a cron to to scan all DS VM records, compare to the real world and apply changes?\n2) can VM.attributes be updated after VM record is created?",
      "range": {
